                    <td>My way to solo Vxed:

Song line up:
_ 4 or 5 dots, it depends on how much you twist.
_ snare
_ Lull (66), if you don't have it, put a mez (65)
_ Mana/heal
_ selo (I use the ornate greaves)

Go see the mob at the exit of the tunnel (blocked zone line) in the water on the right, target him and say: &quot;vxed&quot;

Enter the zone. Levitate yourself (with SS boots), not necessary but really usefull.

The only mobs which will summon you are the stonemites so don't pull them.

I kit at the ...</td>
